# cloudflare-platform

Manage Cloudflare Workers, KV storage and AI Gateway resources.

## MCP Configuration

MCP servers for this plugin are in `.cursor/mcp.json`. Environment variables use `${env:VAR_NAME}` syntax in Cursor.
